org.sakaiproject.content.tool

Class ListItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.content.tool.ListItem

  • public class ListItem
extends Object
    ListItem This class is for displaying a ContentEntity in the user interface. The typical lifecycle of the object is to:
    • Create a new instance of from a ContentEntity using ListItem(ContentEntity).
    • Update the newly created object, probably from a HTTP request captureProperties(ParameterParser, String).
    • Push the changes back to a ContentEntity using updateContentResourceEdit(ContentResourceEdit) so it can be saved.
